Package: dummyscoring
Type: Package
Title: Dummy Extension Scoring
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Paul Keenan
Maintainer: Paul Keenan <paulkeenan02@outlook.com>
Description: Contains just one function, dummy_score(), which takes in a matrix or dataframe and calculates factor scores using Dummy Extension Scoring (Keenan, 2023, not yet published). 
    The method uses 'factor extension' (Gorsuch 1997) to extend loadings to the categories of variables, and then estimates factor scores using those category loadings.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyLoadings: false
ByteCompile: true
Imports: MASS, Matrix, psych, future, future.apply, fastDummies, stats
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
